---
source: crates/biome_html_analyze/tests/spec_tests.rs
expression: valid.vue
---
# Input
```vue
<!-- should not generate diagnostics -->
<video><track kind="captions" /></video>
<audio><track kind="captions" /></audio>
<!-- muted videos don't need captions -->
<video muted></video>
<video muted>
    <source src="video.webm" type="video/webm" />
</video>
<!-- case insensitive kind check -->
<video><track kind="Captions" /></video>
<!-- custom components should be ignored -->
<Video />
<Audio />
<VideoPlayer />
<AudioPlayer />
<!-- static Vue bindings with kind="captions" are valid -->
<video><track :kind="'captions'" /></video>
<audio><track v-bind:kind="'captions'" /></audio>

```
